data.description: Elegant 4-Bed, 3-Bath Home in Belmont, NC**  Discover modern living in this stunning 4-bed, 3-bath home in charming Belmont, NC. With a thoughtfully updated kitchen, this residence combines functionality and style seamlessly. Inside, find spacious, light-filled rooms and an open layout that flows from the kitchen to the living area. The kitchen boasts sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient island with bar seating. Relax in the cozy living room, complete with a fireplace. Step through glass doors to your private backyard deck overlooking the backyard and wooded scenery. Additional features include an attached 2-car garage and a prime Belmont location near schools, shops, dining, and Lake Wylie.  Don't miss the chance to own this Belmont gem!
